\title{Probability Density Functions}
\taxon{definition}

\p{
  For a continuous r.v. #{X} with CDF #{F_X(x)}, the \strong{probability density function} (PDF, 概率密度函数) of #{X} is defined as

  ##{
    f_X(x) = \frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}x} F_X(x)
  }
}

\p{
  Similarly, the \strong{cumulative distribution function} (CDF, 累积分布函数) of #{X} can be obtained by integrating the PDF:

  ##{
    F_X(x) = \int_{-\infty}^x f_X(t) \; \mathrm{d}t
  }
}
